{"tid":406451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普聯合國發言 若美國被迫自衞將「完全消滅北韓」","createTime":"2017-09-19T16:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T00:01:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a45d70ba2f994c1faf6c59b7d45c1c2092950d","tid":406451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170919/large/1505832388_847f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170919%2Flarge%2F1505832388_847f.jpg&h=8d54d278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周二在聯合國大會發言，向與會各國領袖發出警告，揚言如果北韓的核威脅對鄰國產生威脅，美國可能會摧毁北韓。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普指北韓為「墮落的政權」，又形容北韓政袖金正恩「為他本人和其政權進行自殺任務」，「美國擁有強大的實力和耐性，但如果為了保衞自己和盟友，我們別無選擇要完全毁滅北韓。」<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"72bc6571c007130db8f8d11419a964c7480077af","tid":406451,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02265ab177c52d381bbf6e08535e09fadfcb24f2","tid":406451,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"金仔：射落海都唔益你哋"},{"pid":"124bd409162b62caf64e36dc24d6e145837882fe","tid":406451,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"係就快啦 得把口"},{"pid":"10055b24892545d08d4dcca871703248b89c13a4","tid":406451,"uid":94047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"好撚廢 晚晚都咀炮同支那有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be17de1b3b66f8155d9d5ad3c8171fe6e9cfdbef","tid":406451,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"敘利亞都未搞掂<br />\n仲周圍挑戰<br />\n金仔睇死你無料到"},{"pid":"4a9